5 December 2007Government Communication and Information System (GCIS) CEO, Mr Themba Maseko will brief the media on the outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held on Wednesday, 5 December 2007. Minister Buyelwa Sonjica of Minerals and Energy will join the media briefing.The briefing will take place as follows:Date: Thursday, 6 December 2007 (tomorrow) Time: 10h00 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaThere will be a video link to the Imbizo Media Centre, Cape Town. Enquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)